---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Traslados desde Aeropuerto Tenerife Sur | TaxiAir">
    <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1635178082660-c8ab2b003543?q=80&w=2105&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D?q=80&w=2000" 
                alt="Costa de Tenerife con el Teide al fondo" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700/200 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold text-sm mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">
                    Servicio Oficial 24/7
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black leading-tight mb-6">
                    Tu taxi oficial del <span class="text-yellow-400">aeropuerto</span> a tu hotel.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-100 mb-10 max-w-xl">
                    Precios cerrados desde Aeropuerto Tenerife Sur (TFS). Confort y seguridad canaria en cada trayecto.
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <a href="/reservar" class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-950 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-lg focus:ring-4 focus:ring-yellow-200 focus:outline-none">
                        Reservar traslado
                    </a>
                    <a href="/gestion" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border-2 border-white/30 px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-400">
                        Ver mi reserva
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50">
                <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">⏱️</span>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900">Puntualidad Certificada</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Monitorizamos tu vuelo. Si se retrasa, te esperamos sin coste extra.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-yellow-50">
                <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">💰</span>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900">Precio Fijo Canario</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">El precio que ves es el que pagas. Sin taxímetros sorpresa.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50">
                <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</span>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900">Seguridad Total</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Vehículos de alta gama y conductores locales profesionales.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-blue-900 mb-4">Destinos más Populares</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Explora la isla desde el momento en que aterrizas.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 auto-rows-[300px]">
                <div class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-blue-900 shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1662492048065-a96f68506a5d?q=80&w=626&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D?q=80&w=1000" alt="Costa Adeje" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-70" />
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-blue-900 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-8">
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Costa Adeje</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/0 group-hover:text-white/100 transition-all duration-300 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0">
                            Playas exclusivas y resorts de lujo. <br> <strong>Desde 25€</strong>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="md:col-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-blue-800 shadow-lg">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1749387920046-243fe41dd374?q=80&w=1632&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D?q=80&w=1000" alt="Los Cristianos" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform opacity-70" />
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Los Cristianos</h3>
                        <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">Desde 20€</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-blue-800 shadow-lg">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1695218994426-089131e9fb97?q=80&w=1074&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D?q=80&w=1000" alt="Puerto de la Cruz" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform opacity-70" />
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-6">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Puerto de la Cruz</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">El corazón del norte. Desde 90€</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-blue-800 shadow-lg">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551341900-ee1c29a24544?q=80&w=1526&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D?q=80&w=1000" alt="Parque Nacional del Teide" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform opacity-70" />
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-6">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Pico del Teide</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">Traslados a excursiones. Consultar precio.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden" aria-labelledby="flota-title">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 id="flota-title" class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Nuestra Flota Sostenible</h2>
            <div class="flex gap-6 overflow-x-auto pb-8 snap-x snap-mandatory scrollbar-hide">
                <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[300px] md:w-[400px] bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549317661-bd32c8ce0db2?q=80&w=500" alt="Tesla Model 3" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-xl mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Eco Premium (100% Eléctrico)</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Ideal para 4 personas y 3 maletas.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[300px] md:w-[400px] bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549317661-bd32c8ce0db2?q=80&w=500" alt="Mercedes Van" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-xl mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Van de Grupo</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Hasta 8 personas con equipaje deportivo.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-[300px] md:w-[400px] bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549317661-bd32c8ce0db2?q=80&w=500" alt="Taxi Standard" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-xl mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Standard Confort</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Berlina clásica, económica y eficiente.</p>
                </div>
								
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-blue-900 text-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-12 gap-6">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2 text-yellow-400">Lo que dicen los viajeros</h2>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="text-2xl font-bold">4.9/5</span>
                        <span class="text-yellow-400 text-xl" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</span>
                        <span class="text-blue-200">en Google Maps</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="bg-white text-blue-900 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">Escribir reseña</button>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <blockquote class="bg-blue-800 p-8 rounded-2xl relative shadow-lg">
                    <p class="italic mb-6 text-blue-50">"Increíble servicio. Nos esperaban en el aeropuerto con un cartel. El conductor fue súper amable y nos dio recomendaciones de guachinches."</p>
                    <cite class="not-italic flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">M</div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="block font-bold">Marcos Rodríguez</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-blue-300">Hace 2 días</span>
                        </div>
                    </cite>
                </blockquote>
                <blockquote class="bg-blue-800 p-8 rounded-2xl relative shadow-lg">
                    <p class="italic mb-6 text-blue-50">"Muy fácil de reservar. Me enviaron el código por email y el precio fue exactamente el que me dijeron en la web."</p>
                    <cite class="not-italic flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">S</div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="block font-bold">Sarah Jenkins</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-blue-300">Hace 1 semana</span>
                        </div>
                    </cite>
                </blockquote>
                <blockquote class="bg-blue-800 p-8 rounded-2xl relative shadow-lg">
                    <p class="italic mb-6 text-blue-50">"Perfecto para familias. Tenían la silla de bebé preparada tal como pedí en el formulario."</p>
                    <cite class="not-italic flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">C</div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="block font-bold">Carla Soto</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-blue-300">Hace 3 días</span>
                        </div>
                    </cite>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Estilo para ocultar scrollbar en carrusel */
    .scrollbar-hide::-webkit-scrollbar {
        display: none;
    }
    .scrollbar-hide {
        -ms-overflow-style: none;
        scrollbar-width: none;
    }
</style>